  "texts": [
    "The key: give the AI \"insight\" about the student's knowledge and prior experience so that it can effectively tailor the scenario.",
    "Scenario Suggestions.",
    "The AI Mentor then offers students a choice among varied scenarios, giving students agency.",
    "Note that the more the student shares with the AI the more personalized the scenarios may be.",
    "For instance, a student that shares \"I have some experience negotiating\" will be given a choice of standard scenarios, but a student that shares additional context \"I am a medical student and I have some experience negotiating\" will receive scenarios tailored to their interests and background."
  ],
